---
description: Browser UI (apps/web, apps/admin, packages)
globs:
  - apps/web/**/*
  - apps/admin/**/*
  - packages/elvish-ui/**/*
  - packages/elvish-client/**/*
---

Browser clients live under `apps/web` and `apps/admin`. Shared UI in `packages/elvish-ui`; API helpers in `packages/elvish-client` (copied to `apps/*/shared/` on `make static-js`).

Regenerate bundles after editing JSX: `make static-js`. CI verifies `apps/web/dist/` and `apps/admin/dist/` match sources.

**Trust boundaries:** No secrets in bundles; use `elvishApiUrl` / `elvishFetch` for API calls. Operator console is standalone at `apps/admin` (`ELVISH_ADMIN_ORIGIN` in split deploy).
